### Implementation Highlights

**Data-Driven Architecture:**
- **LEFT_TURNS & RIGHT_TURNS maps** - Eliminated duplication by mapping all cardinal directions to their rotated counterparts
- **MOVEMENT_DELTAS map** - Encodes position changes for each direction (N/E/S/W)
- **COMMAND_HANDLERS map** - Unified command dispatch pattern for L/R/F commands

**Refactoring Discipline:**
- Applied all Four Rules of Simple Design at each refactoring phase
- Used APP (Absolute Priority Premise) mass calculations to justify refactoring decisions
- Discovered that data-driven approaches reduced complexity while scaling better for future features

**Files Generated:**
- `src/mars-rover.ts` - Complete implementation with 3 static maps and 4 methods
- `src/mars-rover.spec.ts` - Comprehensive test suite with 18 test cases
- `experiment-done.txt` - Completion marker for automated experiment

The implementation is production-ready with clean, maintainable code that follows TDD best practices.
